Package: RegCompassR
Title: Species-Aware Multiome Reaction Capacity and GRN Meta-Module Analysis
Version: 1.6.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "RegCompass", family = "Developers", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dev@example.com"))
Author: RegCompass Developers [aut, cre]
Maintainer: RegCompass Developers <dev@example.com>
Description: Runs a species-aware human or mouse strict-stratum RNA+ATAC metacell workflow with signed Pando regulatory evidence, conservative GPR aggregation, literature-backed extracellular environments, zero-preserving absolute reaction evidence, local and global FASTCORE completion, persistent shared GEM caches, sample-by-cell-type inference, and directional minimum evidence-discordance scoring.
